Package misux.div.exceptions

Exception Summary
ExecutionException This exception will thrown, if an external command or program will execute from the class Run
MusicIsRippedException This exception will thrown, if the music is already ripped (i.e. the music files are in the music directory.
NoCDException This exception will thrown, if no CD is inserted.
NoCoverFoundException This exception will be thrown, if no picture of the specified album was found.
NoLyricFoundException This exception will thrown, if no lyric was found.
NoOptionExistsException This Exception will thrown, if an option with the same identifier (name) also exists.
SpecialKeyException This TypeIsNotEqualsException will thrown, if a special key was found.
TypeIsNotEqualsException This exception is for the option class.
